            "title": "〈智慧顯示展〉友達彭双浪：中東戰事一天三變 景氣沒年初預期樂觀但也不悲觀",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JXG53QZ.jyJKWgMap9jYuQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/75c1b5a037ef253c6853b5a40a4ed798\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
